Comment: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相识的你捡起
Comment: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交还给我
Comment: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,这么说来　重要的东西
Comment: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:20.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要写上名字
Comment: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:23.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然会丢失于不知何处
Comment: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,经常被这样告诫
Comment: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的错
Comment: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也不属于任何人
