Comment: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,随风　来吧手牵手
Comment: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,于空　配合对方步调
Comment: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出发了
